metadata.description: Cryptorastas Stories #01 is the story of Cryptorasta #03241 - Daryl Pryce is an architect from Negril, Jamaica and can't live without style & fashion.  ☆ This is one of the CRYPTORASTAS STORIES! ☆ Every CryptoRasta has its own unique story.
